Class MeicoApp

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • meico.app.gui.MeicoApp

  • public class MeicoApp
extends javafx.application.Application
    This is a standalone application of meico with a graphical user interface. It is based on JavaFX 2.
